===魔神巡迴演唱會===
{{main|{{tsl|en|The Monster Ball Tour|魔神巡迴演唱會}}}}
卡卡原先計畫與饒舌歌手[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]於巡演{{tsl|en|Fame Kills: Starring Kanye West and Lady Gaga|名望獵物：女神卡卡和肯伊·威斯特主演}}合作<ref name="Fame Kills tour">{{Cite journal|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/fame-kills-starring-kanye-west-and-lady-gaga-tour-first-dates-20090911|title="Fame Kills Starring Kanye West and Lady Gaga" Tour: First Dates|last=Kreps|first=Daniel|date=2009-09-11|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2015-03-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403005818/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/fame-kills-starring-kanye-west-and-lady-gaga-tour-first-dates-20090911|archivedate=2015-04-03}}</ref>
但在與[[泰勒絲|泰勒絲]]引起的[[2009年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎#爭議|2009年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎的糾紛]]後，威斯特宣布他將會暫時離開音樂產業。也因此所有的名望獵物巡迴場次立即取消，而卡卡也表示為了宣傳《超人氣魔神》她將獨自開始巡演。<ref name="ref6">{{Cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1622849/kanye-west-lady-gagas-fame-kills-tour-canceled/|title=Kanye West/ Lady Gaga's Fame Kills Tour Canceled|accessdate=2009-10-01|date=2009-10-01|last=Montogomery|first=James|publisher=MTV|=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302085733/http://www.mtv.com/news/1622849/kanye-west-lady-gagas-fame-kills-tour-canceled/|archivedate=2016-03-02}}</ref>
開始自2009年11月至2011年5月，卡卡將魔神巡迴演唱會形容為「前所未有的電音流行歌劇」。<ref name="bbannounceball">{{Cite news|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lady-gaga-announces-the-monster-ball-tour-20091015|title=Lady Gaga Announces 'The Monster Ball' Tour|accessdate=2009-10-15|date=2009-10-15|last=Kreps|first=Daniel|work=Rolling Stone|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110103215856/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lady-gaga-announces-the-monster-ball-tour-20091015|archivedate=2011-01-03}}</ref> 卡卡和製作團隊在最初製作了適合表演演唱的相框式舞台。她認為這樣的設計能讓她保有創意的掌控。<ref name="insideball" /> 自專輯解決了卡卡過去一年所面對的問題後，在卡卡於巡演行進時對自己轉變的描述下，巡演的主題也跟著轉變為「進化」。表演的歌曲全選自《超人氣》和《超人氣魔神》。<ref name="Monster Ball Tour">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/videos/news/453125/lady-gagas-monster-ball-tour-the-concept.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga's Monster Ball Tour: The Concept|date=2009-11-04|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2009-11-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091108064345/http://www.mtv.com/videos/news/453125/lady-gagas-monster-ball-tour-the-concept.jhtml|archivedate=2009-11-08}}</ref>

對於2010年的場次，卡卡因為巡演的原版本概念構成的時間太短而認為整體需要重新改造。新的主題講述卡卡和她朋友在紐約旅行並前往魔神巡迴演唱會時迷路的故事。<ref name="revamp2">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1632101/lady-gaga-dishes-on-revamped-monster-ball-tour/|title=Lady Gaga Dishes On Revamped Monster Ball Tour|last=Dinh|first=James|date=2010-02-18|accessdate=2010-02-18|publisher=MTV News|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216182946/http://www.mtv.com/news/1632101/lady-gaga-dishes-on-revamped-monster-ball-tour/|archivedate=2015-02-16}}</ref> 包括最後的安可場，演出一共分成5個片段。每個片段都以不同造型的卡卡作為特色並配上了下一段的過場影片。<ref name="sjm">{{cite news|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/2009/12/14/review-lady-gaga-thrills-s-f-crowd-with-strange-sexy-show/|title=Review: Lady Gaga thrills S.F. crowd with strange, sexy show|last=Harrington|first=Jim|date=2009-12-14|work=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]]|accessdate=2009-12-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921071507/http://www.mercurynews.com/2009/12/14/review-lady-gaga-thrills-s-f-crowd-with-strange-sexy-show/|archivedate=2016-09-21}}</ref> 根據全部200場場次報告表示，巡演約有250萬名觀眾，總收入約為2.274億美金，使卡卡成為了巡演總收入最高的新人藝術家。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/photos/live/471708/lady-gagas-monster-ball-tour-breaks-record-for-debut-headlining-artist|title=Lady Gaga's Monster Ball Tour Breaks Record for Debut Headlining Artist|date=2011-12-08|work=Billboard|accessdate=2011-12-27|last=Waddell|first=Ray|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509041933/http://www.billboard.com/articles/photos/live/471708/lady-gagas-monster-ball-tour-breaks-record-for-debut-headlining-artist|archivedate=2013-05-09}}</ref> 其中巡演場次之一，位於紐約市的[[麥迪遜廣場花園|麥迪遜廣場花園]]演唱會由[[HBO|HBO]]轉播為電視特別節目《{{tsl|en|Lady Gaga Presents the Monster Ball Tour: At Madison Square Garden|女神卡卡魔神巡迴演唱會 : 麥迪遜廣場花園}}》。<ref name="Kaufmanspecial">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1658005/lady-gaga-hbo-special/|title=Lady Gaga Announces HBO Monster Ball Special|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=2011-02-15|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2012-03-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906200305/http://www.mtv.com/news/1658005/lady-gaga-hbo-special/|archivedate=2015-09-06}}</ref>

